701274f-a.folder: Holland Avenue & Morris Park Avenue, Bronx, NY
701274f-a.original_title: Bronx: Holland Avenue - Morris Park Avenue
701274f-a.text:
1808 Holland Ave. (left), at the N.E. corner of Morris Park Ave., showing the parochial school of the Church of our Lady of Solace.
July 28, 1928.
P. L. Sperr.

701485f-a.folder: Morris Park Avenue & Holland Avenue, Bronx, NY
701485f-a.original_title: Bronx: Morris Park Avenue - Holland Avenue
701485f-a.text:
Morris Park Avenue, west from Holland Avenue. At the S.E. corner of Hunt (formerly Cruger) Avenue is the old Van Nest Methodist Episcopal Church. A brick edifice later replaced the wooden structure seen in this view.

1913
